                     <interp inst="t18311201-16-off94" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18311201-16-cd95" type="crimeDate">24th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-16-off94 t18311201-16-cd95"></join>, at St. Mary Matfellon, alias Whitechapel, 6 handkerchiefs, value 1l.; 2 shawls, value 8l.; 1 apron, value 3d.; 1 tea-caddy, value 4s.; 2 yards of cambric, value 2s.; 2 razors and case, value 3s.; 1 decanter, value 10s.; 1 snuff-box, value 6d.; 2 brushes, value 1s. 6d.; 1 purse, value 6d.; 3 sovereigns, 8 half-crowns, 15 shillings, 1 sixpence, and 21 1/2d. in copper monies, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18311201-16-victim274" type="victimName">
                           William 
