                     <interp inst="t18311201-16-person277" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was on duty with Arnold - his statement is correct.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM WILKINSON. This is my property, and the shawl it is in - the money is the same as I lost.</p>
               <p>[Dec. 2] <rs id="t18311201-16-verdict99" type="verdictDescription">
